  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Problem\r\n\r\nThere is a specific condition when message unread counter shows in 1-1 chat while all messages are read. \r\nI noticed it reproduced when contact receives message, sends message and then taps 'Add to contacts' (see steps to reproduce)\r\nNote: if for above case this contact sends a couple of messages to buddy in 1-1 then after re-login unread message counter clears. But if to not send - any relogin doesn't make a difference.\r\nAlso, 'Read all messages' options helps in that case.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nNo unread message counter after all message were read\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nUnread message counter persists after relogin after all message were read \r\n\r\n![ezgif-4-aeacae9eb2d5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8749671/89899226-9e20c780-dbea-11ea-9125-90e06e74701c.gif)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Create two new accounts: UserA and UserB\r\n- UserA adds UserB by scanning it's QR code\r\n- UserA taps 'Add to contacts' and sends text message to UserB\r\n- UserB opens 1-1 chat with received message and sends text message to UserA\r\n- UserB taps 'Add to contacts' option\r\n- UserB relogins to account \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n- Status version: release/develop 1.5\r\n- Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\nLogs:\r\n[unreadcounter.txt](https://github.com/status-im/status-react/files/5057222/unreadcounter.txt)\r\n\r\n```\r\n.....\r\n.....\r\n\r\n08-11 16:20:20.306 26167 26278 I ReactNativeJS: INFO [status-im.data-store.mailservers:34] - deleted gaps successfully\r\n08-11 16:20:20.308 26167 26278 W ReactNativeJS: WARN [status-im.ethereum.json-rpc:212] - :json-rpc/error wakuext_markMessagesSeen :error {:code -32000, :message \"sql: Scan error on column index 9, name \\\"last_message\\\": unsupported Scan, storing driver.Value type []uint8 into type *protocol.Message\"} :params [\"0x044db546bb65e4f25fd5d9101c292b8a10a7ca56d849b3f9e286583a2ff6231699c065c710446dcc3ed304f237029f70f15ce4165aa08116c4f4bf838e99e095a8\" #{\"0x736f3e1c34c3e2fb2b160d6a22eb854e8e768c76b15b4aaf319bebd1fd058889\"}]\r\n...\r\n...\r\n...\r\n```",
